data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_8f8f0c70f50a92e500699fd5be4c588190b1ec457c281b2706","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":306,"text":"## Smart Eyewear (Contoso Galaxy Innovations — SmartView Glasses)\n\nThe documentation describes Contoso Galaxy Innovations’ **Smart Eyewear** product (referred to as **SmartView Glasses**) as a pair of connected glasses that combine AR, hands-free assistance, and capture capabilities while still providing traditional eyewear protection features .\n\n### Core features\n- **Augmented Reality (AR) interface**: Provides an AR experience directly through the glasses for interactive, on-the-go use .\n- **Voice-controlled AI agent**: Lets you control functions and interact with an AI assistant hands-free using voice commands .\n- **HD video recording with 3D audio**: Captures high-definition video along with spatial/3D audio for more immersive recordings .\n- **UV protection + blue light filtering**: Adds eye-protection benefits (sun/UV and screen-related blue light reduction) alongside the smart capabilities .\n- **Wireless charging with extended battery life**: Supports convenient charging without cables and is designed for longer runtime .\n\n### What the included user guide emphasizes\nThe guide outline indicates practical coverage for **feature/control overview, sizing & fit adjustments, care/cleaning, an AR “break-in period,” safety tips, and troubleshooting** .\n\nIf you share how you plan to use them (commuting, work calls, content capture, etc.), I can map the features above to the most relevant use cases."}

